{"tid":753004,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"內地政府下令清理中國夢標語","createTime":"2018-07-23T09:16:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-23T10:25:49.000Z","uid":26769,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d6b4b6bf175f7c09cbea04502a4ebef08e964f3e","tid":753004,"uid":26769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T09:16:24.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】國家主席習近平2012年上台後，內地街頭不時會見到他的語錄、畫像，不過近期他的形象工程似乎有所收斂。<br />\n<br />\n南韓《朝鮮日報》報道，北京市等地早前接獲指示拆除習近平的畫像後，再接到通知要求下令清理「中國夢」等與習近平有關的政治標語。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，美國有中文媒體早前取得北京市順義區政府發出的通告，要求在上周五或之前完成清理有與十九大相關口號的橫幅、招牌等宣傳品。<br />\n<br />\n這些宣傳品口號包括：「以習近平新時代中國特色社會主義思想為指導」、「實現中華民族偉大復興的中國」等十五種口號。有分析指，內地當局再次下達指示清理政治標語，原因是中國內部對習近平個人崇拜的反感情緒愈來愈高漲。<br />\n<br />\n早於本月9日，內地官媒《人民日報》的頭版，曾經「破天荒」未有以「習近平」作為標題，為五年來首次。這個情況在12日和15日再度發生，引起外界猜測。<br />\n<br />\n不過有外媒報道指，習近平近期出訪中東、非洲，離開北京十多天，本身已能證明他的地位仍然穩固。"},{"pid":"5cce36d87eba8d58e44181e09653c7e8625e7969","tid":753004,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T09:18:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/171738_ccfe430584717a163a52548274df0980.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F171738_ccfe430584717a163a52548274df0980.png&h=ef911637&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=314004&amp;refer=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D314004%26refer%3Dshare&d=ZxeHy217KvZL1YY2zO4x2V0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=1d167452\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D314004%26refer%3Dshare&h=9c0f929c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=314004&amp;refer=share</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n條片入面啲人好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n拍馬屁拍著馬春袋"},{"pid":"2b375d5a8ce430c8356d2f6bb42b682fd6b97780","tid":753004,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T09:19:30.000Z","msg":"香港班奴才無得邀功了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36e1bc8c71c63b0bca8d2680a461b0712a7a1938","tid":753004,"uid":8410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T09:21:48.000Z","msg":"刁帝登基咁奈仲有人搞到佢咩？ d 對手都俾佢清晒咁濟"},{"pid":"17033714448dd785d582ef9cb2ca167b36a11fff","tid":753004,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b375d5a8ce430c8356d2f6bb42b682fd6b97780","tid":753004,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T09:19:30.000Z","msg":"香港班奴才無得邀功了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T10:25:49.000Z","msg":"香港果班未收到風，不過一帶一路已經講少左。"}]}